  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个支付流程的时序图，展示从用户提交表单到最终通知的完整链路。重点是突出各个基础设施组件的耗时。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "timeline",
        "payment flow",
        "infra components"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。这个时间线是从T0开始吗？还有，标题里要体现IngressController，是因为它作为入口网关比较关键？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T0ms",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，T0毫秒用户提交支付表单，IngressController作为入口。然后T10毫秒Payment service收到请求，这里要拆两个并行检查：RedisCache做幂等性校验5毫秒，LoadBalancer做JWT验证8毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T0ms",
        "T10ms",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "idempotency check",
        "JWT validation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，T25毫秒这里我合并了前面的串行耗时。然后钱包余额检查也是走RedisCache对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T25ms",
        "wallet balance check",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，12毫秒查余额。紧接着资金预留要写到EtcdCluster，15毫秒。这两个加起来同步阶段总共40毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T25ms",
        "reserve funds",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Total sync: 40ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "T50毫秒返回给用户，然后加10毫秒网络延迟，T60毫秒用户看到交易ID和成功状态。这里状态也存RedisCache？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T50ms",
        "T60ms",
        "network latency",
        "Transaction ID",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。然后异步流程开始：T150毫秒风控服务收到事件，这里比较复杂——LoadBalancer查历史数据30毫秒，EtcdCluster跑ML推理40毫秒，还有DynamoDB写入20毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T150ms",
        "Fraud service",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "ML inference",
        "DynamoDB writes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "风控这块总计约90毫秒。接下来T250毫秒Payment service把消息丢到SQS队列，也是走LoadBalancer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T250ms",
        "Payment service",
        "SQS",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。然后T400毫秒银行响应回来，ePayco确认。这里网络往返100毫秒，银行处理100毫秒，响应解析50毫秒，总共约250毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T400ms",
        "Bank",
        "ePayco",
        "network time",
        "bank processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "T420毫秒这里是不是紧接的？交易更新5毫秒，幂等存储10毫秒，SNS发布5毫秒。这个节点和T400毫秒挨得很近。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T420ms",
        "transaction update",
        "idempotency store",
        "SNS publish"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，银行确认后几乎立即更新。然后T500毫秒发通知，走IngressController，邮件和短信都入队。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T500ms",
        "Notifications",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Email",
        "SMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最后T1000毫秒用户刷新App看到\"已确认\"状态。整个流程1秒闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1000ms",
        "User",
        "Confirmed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，T25毫秒那里我漏说了——资金预留是15毫秒，但前面余额检查12毫秒，这两个是串行的，所以T25毫秒这个标记点应该包含这两个操作，而不是从25才开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T25ms",
        "wallet balance check",
        "reserve funds",
        "timing alignment"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，T25毫秒是余额检查的开始点，预留资金紧随其后，到T40毫秒左右完成同步阶段。那T50毫秒返回用户是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
