      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有，标题用\"Timeline de Pago\"吧，业务方是拉美团队，这样更贴近实际。IngressController作为核心入口组件要体现在标题里。",
